title: Bid2Earn Bazaar
body:
Post your auction with an initial bid price. X% of initial bid price deposit required (have minimum price for each level-- low/med/high/degen)

some % deposit to Treasury
some % to Kick off Bid2Earn Incentives
some % to whoever figures out how to make it work
choices: YAAS, MOAR BID, MOAR EARN, MOAR!
